	toFolder = '['+tagProvider+']'
	def getTag(Tag,Path=''):
		tag={}
		tagname = Tag['Tagname']
		baseDerivedTemplate = Tag['BaseDerivedTemplate'].replace('$','')
		tag['name']=tagname
		if len(Path)>0:
			fullPath = Path + '/' + tagname
		objectBaseType = Tag['ObjectBaseType']
		tag["tagType"]='UdtInstance'
		if objectBaseType == '$Area':
			tag["tagType"]='Folder'
		#Map UDT from baseDerivedTemplate
		tags = []
		if baseDerivedTemplate in mapping:
			baseDerivedTemplateObject = mapping[baseDerivedTemplate]
			typeID = baseDerivedTemplateObject['typeId']
			tag['typeID']=typeID
			
			#newtag['parameters'] = newParams
			params = {}
			params['Description'] = Tag['Description']
			tag['parameters'] = params
			
			#Set Attributes
			
			if "Attributes" in baseDerivedTemplateObject:
				#i=l
				attributes = Tag["Attributes"]
				
				for attribute in attributes:
					atrName = attribute['Name']
					mappingAttributes = baseDerivedTemplateObject['Attributes']
					
					if atrName in mappingAttributes:
						tagObject = mappingAttributes[atrName]

#					
#						attributePath = mappingAttributes[atrName]

#							if len(tagsArray) > 0:

#							else:

#							return tagObject

#								tagObject = addFolderTag(tagObject,attributeName)
#							else:
#								tagObject = {"name":attributeName,"tagType": "Folder","tags":[]}
						address = attribute['Address']
						strTagObject = system.util.jsonEncode(tagObject['Configuration'])
						strTagObject = strTagObject.replace("<Address>",address.split('.')[-1])
						tagObject = system.util.jsonDecode(strTagObject)
						tags.append(tagObject)			
						
			tag["tags"]=tags		
		else: #Make It a Folder
			tag["tagType"]='Folder'
		
		
		#Get Children
		children = Tag['Children']
		tags = []
		for child in children:
			childTag = getTag(child)
			tags.append(childTag)
		if len(tags)>0:
			tag['tags'] = tags
		return tag

		fullPath = folderName

			fullPath = path + '/' + folderName

#	 				break
	 			typeId = fullPath+'/'+name

tagProvider = self.view.custom.tagProfider
	toIGN = self.view.custom.toIGN
	toFolder = '['+tagProvider+']'
	collisionPolicy = "a" #Overwrite, "a" #abort
	self.view.custom.response = "Configuring...."
	qualityCodes = system.tag.configure(basePath=toFolder, tags=toIGN,collisionPolicy = collisionPolicy)
	self.view.custom.response = "Configured:" + str(qualityCodes[0])
